[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/46]Fog Be Gone[/url] — dedicated fog remover (plus optional wind/rain off). Use this instead of Show Me Moar's fog toggle if you want more control.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/55]Misc. Bits and Bobs[/url] — "Condense XP Bar", "Remove Cinematic Letterboxing", "Hide Credits Button On Main Menu" and more — pairs with Show Me Moar for a cleaner UI.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/125]Rest In Patches[/url] — vanilla bug fixes including player-movement judder.[/size]
[/list]

